        <a name="003083"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://shellrevealed.com/forums/thread/2509.aspx">shell: revealed - Can&#39;t drag quicklaunch toolbar to top of desktop</a></h4>

        

        <p>I&#8217;m playing with Vista on my laptop, and this &#8220;improvement&#8221; from Microsoft was pissing me off.  Thankfully there is a &#8220;solution&#8221;.  One that is a usability nightmare waiting to happen (drag a folder too close to the edge of the screen, and it becomes a toolbar that is hard to work out how to close).</p>

