        <a name="003080"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.applematters.com/index.php/section/comments/zune-marketplaces-absurd-pricing-scheme/">Apple Matters | Zune Marketplace&#39;s Absurd Pricing Scheme</a></h4>

        

        <p>Microsoft&#8217;s &#8220;you must buy points in $5 increments&#8221; makes sense if you consider credit-card transaction costs (I&#8217;m sure Apple loses money if you only buy one 99 cent song at a time &#8212; that&#8217;s why they batch up your transactions), but the user experience of &#8220;1.25 cents per point&#8221; is ridiculous, and probably going to bite MS.</p>

